#                    authored changesets": desktop-inspired ratatui-
#                    style TUI for reviewing git diff / git show /
#                    git stash / git difftool / raw patch / file-pair
#                    inputs, with multi-file sidebar navigation, inline
#                    AI/agent annotations beside code, split + stack +
#                    auto layouts, watch mode for auto-reload, and a
#                    local Hunk session daemon so AI coding agents
#                    (Claude Code / Codex CLI / Cursor) can read the
#                    user's current review state through a documented
#                    session API rather than blind-firing edits
#                    (TypeScript/Bun, 4554★)
